SELECT COALESCE("DISPLAYNAME", "DISPLAYNAME") AS "DISPLAYNAME", "BADGECOUNT", "QUESTIONCOUNT", "ANSWERCOUNT", "TOTALSCORE", "AVGVIEWCOUNT", CONCAT('Gold: ', CAST("GOLDBADGES" AS VARCHAR CHARACTER SET "ISO-8859-1"), ', Silver: ', CAST("SILVERBADGES" AS VARCHAR CHARACTER SET "ISO-8859-1"), ', Bronze: ', CAST("BRONZEBADGES" AS VARCHAR CHARACTER SET "ISO-8859-1")) AS "BADGESUMMARY"
FROM (SELECT "Users"."Id" AS "ID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", CASE WHEN "t1"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."QUESTIONCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."QUESTIONCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."ANSWERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."ANSWERCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."TOTALSCORE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "TOTALSCORE", CASE WHEN "t3"."AVGVIEWCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."AVGVIEWCOUNT" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "AVGVIEWCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t1"."GOLDBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."GOLDBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDBADGES", CASE WHEN "t1"."SILVERBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."SILVERBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERBADGES", CASE WHEN "t1"."BRONZEBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."BRONZEBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM "STACK"."Users"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT ANY_VALUE("Users0"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users0"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM "STACK"."Users" AS "Users0"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Badges" ON "Users0"."Id" = "Badges"."UserId"
GROUP BY "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."DisplayName") AS "t1" ON "Users"."Id" = "t1"."USERID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "OwnerUserId" AS "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "ANSWERCOUNT", SUM("Score") AS "TOTALSCORE", AVG("ViewCount") AS "AVGVIEWCOUNT", COUNT(DISTINCT "Tags") AS "UNIQUETAGCOUNT"
FROM "STACK"."Posts"
GROUP BY "OwnerUserId") AS "t3" ON "Users"."Id" = "t3"."OWNERUSERID") AS "t4"
WHERE "t4"."BADGECOUNT" > 0